reviewText: A friend of mine has this movie. I've enjoyed watching it over and over. I had to buy my own copy but it's very hard to find. I was lucky that this seller had a BluRay version available. Shipping from Japan to the US was a little long, but well worth it. I now own a copy of this fantastic short.
